docs.snippet: St. Louis rookie Michael Wacha pitched seven innings and drove in two runs, helping the Cardinals to a 5-3 victory Thursday afternoon over the Chicago Cubs....
docs.lead_paragraph: St. Louis rookie Michael Wacha pitched seven innings and drove in two runs, helping the Cardinals to a 5-3 victory Thursday afternoon over the Chicago Cubs.

headline.main: Wacha Sparks Cardinals in Win Over Cubs
